//- [data-nav] attribute will append section as a nav link in the header bar
section.about-us(data-nav='About Us')

	+subtitle('About Us')

	.brand-value-imgs
		svg.crop-tier-2(viewBox='0 0 240 381'): use(xlink:href='#crop-tier-2')
		.brand-value-imgs-wrap.clear
			each value, i in brandValues
				- title = value.title.toLowerCase()
					.brand-value-img(data-value=title, data-i=i)
						svg(viewBox='0 0 1500 970')
							image(
								width='1500',
								height='970',
								x='0',
								y='0',
								xlink:href='src/img/brand-values-' + title + '.jpg'
							)

	.brand-value-copy
		.brand-value-copy-wrap
			each value, i in brandValues
				- title = value.title.toLowerCase()
				.brand-value-txt(data-value=title, data-i=i)
					each desc, i in value.desc
						if i === 0
							p(data-txt)= desc
							h3.title.crop(data-txt)= value.title
						if i === 1
							p(data-txt)= desc

	h2.brand-values-big-title.crop Audacious Kindred Magentic Inspired
	.brand-txt
		.wrap.clear
			.col-5.before-2
				p(data-txt) Founded in 2000, DeviantArt is the leading online community and social network for artists and visual enthusiasts. The company aggregates and distributes more original artist-generated content than any other site. It offers artists and fans of all interests an opportunity to communicate through art, share their passions for pop culture, and engage as part of a global collective.
				p(data-txt) #[a.link(href='http://spyed.deviantart.com/journal/Boldly-Facing-The-Future-498282387', target='_blank') Learn About Our Story]